-- Rothschild Advising Unicredit, Italpetrolio on Sale of Soccer Club AS Roma
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-07-27T06:24:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/rothschild-advising-unicredit-italpetrolio-on-sale-of-soccer-club-as-roma.html

          
          
             Rothschild SpA will advise UniCredit
SpA and Compagnia Italpetroli SpA on the sale of the soccer team
AS Roma SpA, Italpetroli said in a stock exchange statement late
yesterday.  
 Italpetroli, the owner of the soccer team, signed yesterday
an agreement to settle its debt with Unicredit. AS Roma was put
on sale by a new company formed by Unicredit and Italpetroli.  
          
          


  


        